# Supabase (login / signup étudiants)
# Google OAuth: Supabase Dashboard → Authentication → Providers → Google
#   Enable Google + add OAuth client ID/secret from Google Cloud Console
#
# URL Configuration (CRITICAL — otherwise Google redirects to localhost):
#   Site URL:        https://belkou.online
#   Redirect URLs:   https://belkou.online/auth/callback
#                    http://localhost:8080/auth/callback
#
# Email confirmation — sender "BelKou" (not "Supabase Auth"):
#   Supabase Dashboard → Authentication → Emails → SMTP Settings
#   → Enable Custom SMTP, then:
#     Sender name:  BelKou
#     Sender email: profzoula@gmail.com
#     Host:         smtp.gmail.com
#     Port:         465  (si 587 échoue, essayez 465 avec SSL)
#     Username:     profzoula@gmail.com
#     Password:     Google App Password (https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords)
#   Si aucun email n'arrive: Supabase → Logs → Auth (erreurs SMTP)
#   Rate limit initial: ~30 emails/heure sur nouveau SMTP
#   Then Authentication → Emails → Templates → Confirm signup:
#     Subject: Confirmez votre compte BelKou
#
# Railway deploys via Dockerfile (FFmpeg installed in image).
# Video HLS worker — enabled by default; set ENABLE_VIDEO_WORKER=false to disable.
# VIDEO_WORKER_POLL_MS=60000
# Railway Variables (required):
#   VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://jxubkuskszpzsllkbmzv.supabase.co
#   VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=<anon key from Supabase API>
#   VITE_SITE_URL=https://belkou.online
#   SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=<service_role key — server only, never VITE_*>
# Dockerfile build fails if VITE_SUPABASE_* are missing at build time.
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://jxubkuskszpzsllkbmzv.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your_anon_key
VITE_WHATSAPP_GROUP_PREMIUM=https://chat.whatsapp.com/J4iP9lv5gYlHrWiLXHuNgD
VITE_WHATSAPP_GROUP_VIP=https://chat.whatsapp.com/GqWxIE5pfafFOB3krHd0uA
# VITE_COHORT_START_DATE= (legacy — no longer shown on the public site)
# VITE_STATS_STUDENTS_BASE=2785
# Stripe price IDs (optional — fallback amounts used if empty)
VITE_STRIPE_PRICE_PREMIUM=
VITE_STRIPE_PRICE_VIP=

